[A total of 7 cases have now been diagnosed in the area. It looks like
there is a limited and local transmission going on. It is comforting that
the 2 new cases are close to Lake Worth. A survey on semi-immune immigrants
from _P. vivax_-endemic countries who may be asymptomatic carriers and thus
act as a reservoir is probably the best approach to identify the source.
Non-immunes will develop symptoms quickly and be treated before they can
contribute to transmission. - Mod.EP]
